# URL of the in-game screenshot used as the ChatPreview backdrop.
#
# The image is licensed game content and must not be committed to the repo.
# Drop your own screenshot into `public/` (e.g. `public/chat-preview-bg.png`)
# and point this variable at it. Any absolute URL also works (e.g. CDN link).
#
# Leave unset / empty to render the fallback placeholder.
NUXT_PUBLIC_CHAT_PREVIEW_BG=/chat-preview-bg.png
